OL,3,CTeacher relives moment of alleged
OL,4,Ckitchen knife attack everyday, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA teacher who was allegedly stabbed in
OL,8,Fthe head by a pupil has told a court
OL,9,Fshe thought she was dying in the
OL,10,Fmoments immediately after the incident.
OL,12,FVicki Williams, a history teacher at
OL,13,FMilford Haven Comprehensive School
OL,14,Ftold Swansea Crown Court that she
OL,15,Frelives the moment everyday in her
OL,16,Fhead.
OL,18,FMs Williams was called to give
OL,19,Fevidence on the second day of the
OL,20,Ftrial.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783678766
OL,3,CTeacher relives moment of alleged
OL,4,Ckitchen knife attack everyday, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe told the jury that her immediate
OL,8,Finstinct after the alleged attack was
OL,9,Fto seek first aid help.
OL,11,FRecalling the moment the defendant
OL,12,Fallegedly lunged for her with a
OL,13,Fkitchen knife, Ms Williams said the
OL,14,Flook in the student's eyes is not
OL,15,Fsomething she is "going to forget very
OL,16,Fquickly", adding they were "full of
OL,17,Fhatred".
OL,26,@yD@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
