OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783678766
OL,3,CTeacher relives moment of alleged
OL,4,Ckitchen knife attack everyday, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe 16-year-old defendant, who we
OL,8,Fcannot name due to legal reasons,
OL,9,Fpreviously pleaded not guilty to the
OL,10,Fthree charges he faces- attempted
OL,11,Fmurder, unlawful wounding, and
OL,12,Fwounding with intent to cause grievous
OL,13,Fbodily harm.
OL,15,FMatthew Roberts KC (defending)
OL,16,Fquestioned Ms Williams on some of the
OL,17,Fdetails surrounding the incident.
OL,19,FMr Roberts asked whether there had
OL,20,Fever been a "falling out" between her
OL,21,Fand the boy.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783678766
OL,3,CTeacher relives moment of alleged
OL,4,Ckitchen knife attack everyday, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMs Williams responded: "Not as far as
OL,8,FI recall. I believe I got on well with
OL,9,Fhim".
OL,11,FThe defence later argued that Ms
OL,12,FWilliams sustained her injuries during
OL,13,Fa scuffle after she tried to
OL,14,Fconfiscate the knife.
OL,16,FThe teacher denied that version of
OL,17,Fevents.JMr Roberts said "There comes a
OL,18,Fpoint you ask him 'what's that in your
OL,19,Fbag?"
OL,26,@oD@XOUqD@DO]yD@YOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783678766
OL,3,CTeacher relives moment of alleged
OL,4,Ckitchen knife attack everyday, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMs Williams responded "No, that is not
OL,8,Fwhat happened".JHe later added "It is,
OL,9,Fthen he took out the knife".
OL,11,FShe replied "That is absolutely not
OL,12,Fwhat happened".
OL,14,FMr Roberts said "You then act
OL,15,Finstinctively and grab the blade with
OL,16,Fboth hands".
OL,18,FMs Williams answered "That is not what
OL,19,Fhappened".
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@NO]pD@`OUqD@[O]sD@MOUtD@NO]vD@
OL,26,AQOUxD@KO]zD@VOU{D@IO]
