PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783678766
OL,3,CTeacher relives moment of alleged
OL,4,Ckitchen knife attack everyday, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FLater in the day, Catherine Wilcox,
OL,8,Fthe safeguarding lead at the school
OL,9,Fgave evidence before the court.
OL,11,FShe recalled seeing Ms Williams and Ms
OL,12,FWilliams' husband alongside police
OL,13,Fofficers at the school, at
OL,14,Fapproximately 17:30 on the evening of
OL,15,Fthe alleged attack.
OL,17,FMs Wilcox was visibly emotional and
OL,18,Ftearful when describing what she saw,
OL,19,Fin front of the jury.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
