PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783678766
OL,3,CTeacher relives moment of alleged
OL,4,Ckitchen knife attack everyday, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe said that her colleague (Ms
OL,8,FWilliams) "looked horrific, her skin
OL,9,Fwas the colour of a dead body. The
OL,10,Fcolour had absolutely gone from her.
OL,11,FHer hair was wild".
OL,13,FShe added: "Vicki always presents
OL,14,Fherself so well, and she looked
OL,15,Fhorrific".
OL,17,FThe court was also shown a timeline of
OL,18,FCCTV footage showing the defendant on
OL,19,F5 February, in the hours and later
OL,20,Fminutes leading up to the alleged
OL,21,Fincident.
OL,26,@pD@KOUsD@RO]uD@LOU
